                  "name": "aboutSummary2",
                  "fill": "$--text-secondary",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "Currently Head of AI & Data Engineering at Devera, where I architect scalable AI services and multi-agent systems. Previously built healthcare AI at Remote Care Partners — patient monitoring, predictive models, and real-time biosignal pipelines.",
